Text: RE Ill be thereIm glad you can make it To get to the OU course from I take State Highway East toward campus Exit left North on Jenkins Go past Lloyd Noble Center and turn right at signal light on Constitution Go about mile and turn left onto Par Drive They will start serving lunch about and will put out range balls before then Some people start showing up around or earlier to hit balls before lunch Ill be there much earlier We have a shotgun start at FYI The following Sig Eps are currently signed up to play You me Chris Walker Jon Armstrong Craig Perkins Scott Smith David Newman Scott Weed Greg Dial Bruce Kennedy Todd Skinner Brian Cain Kevin Holland Thomas Burleson Rick Sheer John Payne Brad McNeese Jeff James Bradley Watson Bradford Watson Joe Ong Chip Long Chris Papasarantou Brad Culver Jeff Marley and Brad Schick Usually playing who I have yet to hear from are Jeff Black Brent McCutcheon Daryl Deaton Russ Brudner Craig Dean Terry Mosslander and a couple of other younger guys See you Friday Donald B Lynn Esq Court of Civil Appeals Original Message From McConnell Mark mailto Sent Tuesday September AM To Subject Ill be there I have arranged to take off this Friday so I will be able to attend I guess Ill get the directions to the golf course and other details from Weed and Dial If the teams are all full put me on their team Otherwise Ill play with anyone My game has gone down the tubes since I started the international work I hope to take care of that problem soonput me down as a handicap I look forward to seeing you and the rest of the guys
